# ===============================

# Reddit API Keys (Required for WSB agent)
# Get your keys at: https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps
REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=
REDDIT_USER_AGENT=Ritadel:v1.0 (by /u/YourUsername)

